name: McKinneyAvenueTrolley
0:
”Alexa, Ask McKinney Avenue Trolley, Where can I catch a trolley right now?”
”Alexa, Ask McKinney Avenue Trolley, Are there any Trolleys running?”
”Alexa, Ask McKinney Avenue Trolley, Where are the Trolleys located currently?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: mckinney avenue trolley
des: Riding on the free McKinney Ave Trolley in Dallas, Texas? With this skill you will know whether there are any trolleys running, and which stops you can catch the next one at. Simply ask Alexa questions like "Where can I catch a trolley right now?" or "Are there any Trolleys running?"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
